<div class="inner" id="msg_963546">*&nbsp; 译名随时都会变动。（有changelog的！）<br>**&nbsp; 因为只有我一个人翻译，而且我翻多少就发多少，所以目录里的进度也就是整个翻译的进度。<br>*** 或许我应该搞个短扩合集帖，但手头一个字翻译也没有就先算啦！<br>**** 存个档：网团用工具：https://spirecompanion.com/<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>changelog</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">05.19, 20：把the works和the garden district改掉了。the garden district是因为它其实不是花园而是菜园（但菜园区太难听了）；the works则是为了对仗（什么？）<br><br>04~05, 20：翻新了职业名。<br></div></div></div><img src="https://i.imgur.com/FBaJLkH.png?1" alt="" height="450" class="bbc_img resized"/><br><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=105301" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">地图</a><br><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=105283" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">欢迎来到高塔 / Welcome to Spire</a><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=105290.0" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">高塔世界 / The World of Spire</a><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=105303.0" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">规则 / The Rules</a><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=107500.0" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">技能与领域 / Skills and Domains</a><br><a href="http://www.goddessfantasy.net/bbs/index.php?topic=117483.